Class DefaultPooledCursors

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.newapi.DefaultCursors
      • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.newapi.DefaultPooledCursors
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CursorFactory
    public class DefaultPooledCursors
extends DefaultCursors
implements CursorFactory
    Cursor factory which pools 1 cursor of each kind. Not thread-safe at all.
